Welcome to the most cosmic game in our galaxy and join us on the space adventure. Jet Pack Dash 2 will take you millions of light years away straight to a spaceship. You are an astronaut whose task is to go from one end of the ship to the other. It only looks easy. Traps and other hazards are waiting for you in the maze of the corridors. You will need dexterity and reflex to complete the mission safely.

- Your task is to go from one end of the ship to the other
- Traps and other hazards are waiting for you in the maze of the corridors
- Use your dexterity and reflex to complete the mission safely

title: Shaggy & The Ghost Blocks
description:
Help Shaggy escape from the haunted building!

While on one of their intrepid adventures, Shaggy finds himself trapped in a haunted building. Fortunately Ghost Blocks are falling from the sky. Use the Ghost Blocks to build a structure so Shaggy can get out. Assembling the structure may look easy, but it must be balanced or it may fall to the ground!

- 54 fun achievements
- 4 misterious worlds
- 3 difficulty modes
- Surprising bombs and ghosts

title: Stack
description:
Start stacking up!

Build the tallest skyscraper by placing each new shape perfectly on top of the previous one. Stack up the blocks to get as high as you can! Timing is everything! Release each piece at the right moment to complete a new layer. If your timing is off, the next piece will be smaller than the last! Enjoy colourful shapes and backgrounds that change as you go higher.

- 30 designs for landscapes and blocks
- Minimalist and beautiful graphics
- Smooth skills game

title: Cut the Rope
description:
Cut the rope to feed candy to little monster Om Nom!

A mysterious package has arrived, and the little monster inside has only one request… CANDY! Collect gold stars, discover hidden prizes and unlock exciting new levels in this addictively fun, award-winning, physics-based game!

- Innovative physics gameplay
- Adorable character
- Outstanding graphics

title: Sweet Bubble Story
description:
Little Fluffy needs your help! His family was captured after crash landing on the Candy Planet. Shoot and match colourful candies to progress further. Overcoming various obstacles to free them you will enter the tasty world of candy, chocolate and the goofy indigenous! Can you free all family members and collect all items needed to progress to the end?

- Classic bubble-style matching arcade
- Dozens of puzzling levels to solve and earn stars of mastery
- Various game modes and obstacles
- Useful booster candies to handle tough situations
- A land full of amusing sceneries and characters

title: God of Light
description:
Play the game that rethinks the physics puzzle genre!

Sit back and become immersed into the world of God of Light, the game that rethinks the physics puzzle genre with its unique environment exploration gameplay, amazing graphics and exclusive soundtrack created by electronic music icon UNKLE. Join cute game mascot, Shiny, on his way to saving the universe from the impending darkness.

- 150 levels of mind-blowing puzzles
- 6 exciting game types
- Beautiful mysterious design

title: Around the World in 80 Days
description:
Phileas Fogg, a British gentleman, is to make it around the world in 80 days. Jean Passepartout, his French servant, is going with him. But Fix, a police inspector, has to keep close track of the travellers, as they are suspected to be the thiefs of the Bank of England. Will Fogg win the bet? Help him surmount the obstacles! To win the bet, you will have to be courageous, to carefully observe things around you and be clever! Elude traps, save an Indian widow, find your way in the jungle, and during longer trips, prove your whilst opponents that cards don’t have any secrets for you! Discover incredible sceneries: London, Suez, Bombay, Calcutta, Hong Kong, Yokohama, San Francisco. And use different transportation means, sometimes very surprising: catch a train, go aboard a ship, travel on the back of an elephant!

- 22 places to visit
- Mini-games: maze, cards games
- Search of objects (list, identical objects)
- Help with zoom on selected screens, limited number of reloading hints, bonus stars

title: Dragons Empire TD
description:
Dragon Queen Liza has a best-kept secret which is a majestic jewel from the outer world. Shimaroo the evil wizard needed the jewel to crown his Wand and acquire its power to rule the all four worlds. So he sent his minions to bring him the jewel or... to die trying. But the wise queen already knew the evil plans of Shimaroo and have hidden the precious stone in dense forest and secured it with magical dragon guards. It’s a time when Vikings have attacked to get the precious Jewel.  Guard and protect the jewel from enemies with the help of dragons. Dragons Empire has the best elements of defence games as well as it includes the original feature of controlling the dragons and real-time strategy elements. Control your dragons to move to the key points. Upgrade to make them stronger. Use power-ups to stop the enemy from stealing the treasure and ultimately the Jewel to make your queen proud. Get the best dragon game now!

- 50 different challenges
- Numerous options to develop strategies
- Awesome graphics

title: Jetpack Soldier
description:
Fly this Soldier geared with a powerful jetpack! Sharp reflexes are your best weapon to avoid the obstacles in your path. Choose between different modes and try to fly as far as you can! Collect coins to get extra points and pickup boosters like bikes, UFOs and vehicles for some extra action! Beware of cans, laser fences and enemies and fly your way through increasing difficult level!

- Tap the screen to ascend and release to descend
- Challenge mode and Quick play mode
- Get a boost of speed by collecting coins and get into supersonic mode

title: My Talking Tom
description:
Nurture your very own Tom and watch him grow!

Adopt your very own baby kitten and help him grow into a fully grown cat. Take good care of your virtual pet, name him and make him part of your daily life by feeding him, playing with him and nurturing him as he grows. Dress him up any way you like and pick from a wide selection of fur colors and other accessories. Decorate his home and travel the world to meet other Toms. Play mini-games and watch as Talking Tom becomes part of your everyday life.

Over 1000 combinations of furs, clothing and furniture
999 levels unlocking new items and coins as you go
Over 10 mini-games: Happy Connect, Bubble Shooter, Planet Hop and more
9 different stages

title: Brutus & Futée
description:
Brutus and Futée are comics strips characters. They used to be famous for their adventures in an old cartoon until their creator disappeared whereas they were at the climax of their success. With no roles to perform any longer, they moved to a quiet township. Now, living a boring life and spending all their days watching TV, they miss their past life full of fun. One day, Futee is mysteriously victim of a gag. Have they found a new author?

- 12 chapters full of humour  
- Interact with the environment and see how the characters react accordingly 
- Greatly animated characters, halfway between the video game and an animated serie

title: Drag Racing Classic
description:
Do you dream about seeing 1000+ HP exotics pushed to the limit on a drag strip?
Would you pick an iconic Skyline GT-R, a classic 69' Mustang, or a brand new BMW M4 as your ultimate driving machine? Buy your dream car, install performance upgrades and show your skills in 1/4 or 1/2 mile races. Do you think racing in a straight line is easy? Try to find the right balance between power and grip while staying in your class. Tune your car and accelerate your way to victory, add nitrous oxide for more fun, but don't hit the button too early! Go deeper and adjust gear ratios to shave off precious milliseconds through 10 levels of cars and race categories.

"50+ real cars including BMW, Dodge, Honda, Nissan, McLaren, Pagani and the officially licensed 1200 bhp Hennessey Venom GT™
Buy performance upgrades, customize and tune your cars
Tune your car and adjust gear ratios for maximum performance"

title: Akinator
description:
Akinator, the Web Genius that reads your mind!
Akinator can read your mind and tell you who you’re thinking of by answering a few questions. Think about a real or fictional character, and he will try to guess who it is! As soon as the genie gets the answer, he will show you a picture of your character. Let him know if he got the correct character or not and keep score. Have fun trying to challenge the Akinator's powers! Think of forgotten characters that will put the Akinator to the test and give you various awards.

6 AkiAwards for challenging the Akinator
Various enchanting backgrounds
Accessories to customize Akinator
Powerful potions to unlock new characters

title: The Three Musketeers
description:
D'Artagnan leaves his native Gascony to join the Royal Guard of the musketeers in Paris! The journey promises to be eventful for this young and impetuous adventurer. Along the way, he meets Athos, Porthos and Aramis, musketeers of King Louis XIII. United by strength, these 4 protagonists set out together on this adventure. Pit your wits against the Machiavellian plans of Cardinal Richelieu, find the Queen's diamonds and save the honour of France!

- 40 locations to explore
- Mini-games: puzzles, reflex games
- Object searches (lists, identical objects)
- Magnificent decor: high-resolution images

title: Treasure Island: The Golden Bug
description:
1827 - William Legrand, son of a fallen family, came to Sullivan Island, South Carolina, to flee the misery. Wandering on the island, he discovers a rare bug, made of gold. He uses a piece of paper to take it. At night, he draws the bug on this same piece of paper, as he is explaining the adventure to his friend Edgar, standing in front of the fireplace. As William takes back the paper, he realises that symbols appeared on it. It must be an invisible ink, revealed by the heat. From that moment, William thinks it is a Pirate’s document: Captain Kidd’s coded instructions to his hidden treasure… Help William find it!

- 18 places to observe
- Mini-games: decipher a coded message, find your way thanks to a compass
- Search of objects (list, identical objects)
- Magnificent sets: high-resolution images

title: Tap the Frog
description:
Ribbit! Jump in and get tapping!
Do you have what it takes to help the Frog jump, paint and spacewalk the way to his sweetheart? Everyone’s favorite Frog is on a mission to become a Frog Prince! Join the Frog as he embarks on an adventure that will take him from the lily pads of his home pond to the farthest reaches of outer space. Easy to play yet challenging to master, Tap the Frog will keep you entertained forever. Let’s see how fast you really are!

27 frogtastic mini-games
Bright and lovely visuals
Gameplay that's easy to pick-up yet challenging to master

title: Powerpuff Girls: Flipped Out!
description:
Save the day with the Powerpuff Girls!

What happens when you overfeed a cute little Sea Buddy pet? TOO MANY SEA BUDDIES! Help Blossom, Bubbles and Buttercup protect the city from an army of adorable monsters in this all-new, fully voiced Powerpuff adventure! It's not a hybrid game—it's two awesome ways to play! Flip to SUGAR mode and use your wits to match same colored creatures until they explode. Or flip to SPICE mode and use your fists to battle the beasts in hand-to-hand combat. It's like two games in one! Change between puzzle and action modes at any time just by flipping your device. You can play exclusively in your favorite mode, or use a combination of brains and brawn for some super synergy! Both modes let you play as Blossom, Bubbles and Buttercup, all at the same time! Team up to take down toughies, or divide and conquer to cover more ground. Unleash spicy and sweet superpowers to demolish the bad guys! It's flipping awesome!

2 modes: match 3 puzzles and action-packed melee
Unlock stickers to upgrade your stats
Add new powers to your arsenal

title: Lion Kingdom
description:
Is the kingdom of lions safe enough for a cute and perfectly innocent young lion?

Get ready to live exciting adventures next to your new friend, the little lion. Help him to reach the title of the king of the jungle sorting all kind of obstacles in this endless run game. Collect orbs, fruits, and bananas to increase your energy bar to be able to sprint for a short period of time. Use the sprints wisely as you may need them for jumping higher and cross rock gaps or avoid an avalanche. Meet other animal kingdom friends; they will help you to overcome all kind of obstacles. Your can friend will carry you, and you’ll be able to fly! Use your power-dash to dodge falling rocks and or low trees. Enjoy playing this new adventure game and help the lion to roar!

Meet Hilarious Animal Characters
Easy One Thumb Controls
HD Smooth Graphics
Tons of Levels and Challenges

title: Sky Blocks Pusher
description:
Become brainy by solving these tricky puzzles!

Enhance your skills and mental ability with Sky Blocks Pusher. This is a blocks based puzzle game, which involves in pushing a set of blocks in a specific direction with the help of Push Bot and placing them in their respected position. Swipe Left/Right/Up/Down to control the movement of Push Bot. You have only one undo option in case if you make a mistake, so don't waste your chance!

50 levels of pushing blocks
Brain teasing puzzle
Fresh cartoonish graphics

title: Link Twin
description:
Discover an innovative puzzle concept!

Link Twin is an exciting and stylistic puzzle game with fresh mechanics, visually stunning art and a haunting soundtrack. Take control of the mysterious Tom and Lily who share an unbreakable connection. Uncover a treacherous world of mysterious landscapes and mind-bending puzzles as you navigate ever increasing challenges. Swipe the screen to move Tom & Lily simultaneously. Use the environment and interactive objects to manipulate positioning and find the exits!

- 100 levels of increasingly challenging puzzle gameplay
- 10 unique mechanics like movable obstacles, teleporters and electronic circuits
- 5 mysterious settings,each with their own haunting soundtrack
- A whole new world of minimalistic art and surreal environments

title: Stick Hero
description:
Be a hero and mind the gap!

It's time to prove your skills and be a stick hero! Stretch the stick in order to reach and walk on the platforms. Watch out! If the stick is not long enough, you will fall down! Pick as many cherries along the way to unlock new characters. If that is not enough for you, try the Watermelon mode! You will get to smash some watermelons with your stick and then jump forward, but be careful not no strike the next platform! How far can you go, stick hero?

- 24 types of heroes
- 2 play modes
- Beautiful and minimalist landscapes
- Intuitive gameplay

title: Mega Spinner
description:
Swipe and spin out of control!

Feeling bored or restless? Enjoy the popular fidget spinner with this fun simulator! Swipe your finger 5 times each round to create the fastest spin ever. Collect points and get upgrades to increase the maximum speed. Want to go even faster? Grease the mechanism for less friction and make physics work in your favour. Customize your spinner and choose from various beautiful designs, with different shapes and colours.

30 fun spinner designs
4 colourful and unique backgrounds
Rotations per minute counter
Realistic physics

title: Jetpack Disco Mouse
description:
Jetpack Disco Mouse needs your help to create the perfect disco party for a mouse and his friends!

Everyone knows mice can’t fly, but Disco Mouse is fully equipped with a state-of-the-art jetpack capable of blasting through farmyards and woodland as he busts his disco moves. Of course no woodland is without its fair share of creatures and hazards to dodge, so be careful to stay out of trouble or you could lose your groove. Control is easy: tap the screen to provide thrust, or hit boost to dodge obstacles and smash through the scenery. Collect musical notes to perform dance moves and come one step closer to the glittering ‘super boost’. Fill the groove meter to complete the level, or take on special missions to win delicious party snacks which must be flown back to the giant disco ball. That’s no mean feat; even a strawberry can be a weighty struggle when you’re a mouse!

- Mice, music, snacks, and a massive disco ball
- Enhanced 3D graphics including depth of field and parallax motion
- Hundreds of stunning countryside levels with dramatic lighting and weather
- Beautifully intuitive controls
- Fight back with a range of power-ups to deploy

title: Fling Monster
description:
Get ready to fling your angry monster army!

The astronauts have invaded Planet X to mine the monsters’ powerful energy crystals. Take down their defences with your awesome slingshot skills and a huge arsenal of 10 different monsters with super mind-blowing abilities. Slingshot your monsters and kill two birds with one stone by creating amazing chain reactions in the beautiful world of Planet X. Use your slingshot to fling each monster at the invading astronauts. Choose your ammo order for maximum effect and try out the awesome flappy monster and tap to keep that monster bird afloat. So come on and help the legendary heroes embark on the adventure of a lifetime. Fling your monsters and blast those pesky astronauts and their big boss machines off the face of Planet X. Join the monster resistance today!

- 140 levels across stunning landscapes like Grasslands, Ice, Desert, Tropical and Lava
- 6 different worlds to explore
- Crazy real world physics based gameplay
- Huge chain reactions and awesome fights
- Large range of ammo like homing missile monster, flappy monster bird, thruster, sticky bomb, momentum bomb and more

title: Freeze! 2 - Brothers
description:
Save your brother from the aliens!

Many years ago, our old hero from „Freeze!“ was kidnapped from evil aliens and locked in a tiny cell on a planet far, far away. He never found his way back. Now his little brother heads to the stars in his self-built rocket to find his lost brother and to free him from the clutches of the aliens! You’ll solve twisted physics-based puzzles by rotating the cells around our heroes with your finger. And of course you’ll have to use the Freeze buttons to arrest gravity for the brothers. Sounds simple? Well, yes, it is - at first.

100 varied and exciting levels
4 alien worlds
New look and unique graphics
Simulation of fluids such as water and deadly rocket fuel
New dark tracks

title: Graffiti Grinder
description:
Spray away and watch out for the Anti-Graffiti Squad!

Make your mark as you jump, glide and dive through the city, tagging over rival squad graffiti and dodging the Anti-Graffiti squad. Grind through colourful city areas! Jump and dive to tag and dodge traps. Take advantage of upgradeable power-ups for high score chasers! Grab a can of spray paint and GO!

- 30 adventurous challenges
- 4 fun power-ups: Coin Magnet, Shield, x2 Jump, x2 Coins
- Endless runner adventure
- Cool and colourful graphics

title: Puzzledrome
description:
Make every row and column a palindrome in as few moves as possible!

Challenge your mind with a game that takes thought, agility, and creative thinking to solve unique palindrome puzzles. Swap the tiles until all of the rows and columns are palindromes, in as few moves as possible. Inspired by symmetry, Sudoku and matching games, Puzzledrome takes tiled based puzzling to the next level! What’s left is right, what’s up is down… Puzzledrome provides the perfect balance of brain teasing challenge and easy to learn puzzling for a captivating game experience you'll want to enjoy again and again. Swipe tiles around until everything lines up just right and you see a perfect palindrome where the tile sequence is the same left to right and up and down. Starting off with a single row of colorful icons, the game teaches you as you go and encourages creativity as you swipe tiles right and left, putting everything in its place. Getting progressively harder, Puzzledrome introduces unique challenges like the shape shifter, stone, and danger tiles that add difficulty to the game.

- 131 challenging puzzles
- 2 speed game modes to challenge yourself: Arcade and Free Play
- Special tiles to add difficulty
- Minimalist and colourful design

title: Cowboy vs UFOs
description:
Would you like to visit the moon or an alien planet?

The Wild West is under alien attack from Dark Space! Wanted cool gunslinger! Maybe you are the space cowboy who can save the Wild West before it’s too late! Fight the UFO invasion as cowboy legend Johnny Wrangler, before the space aliens succeed with their dastardly plan! Shoot quickly, but accurately space UFOs: this is a real cowboy shooter game with cool guns!

- 20 types of guns for real cowboys
- 8 space UFOs with unique behaviors and characteristics
- Crazy and funny endless UFO shooter
- Western style and cowboy country music

title: Hectic Gates
description:
Jump through the gates!

Make your way through the colorful but dangerous gates. Just tap anywhere on the screen to jump. Try to pass through the different types of gates. Plan your jumps carefully and try to sneak between the obstacles at any cost or you will have to start again. Play and unlock different types of gates and characters. Don't get too frustrated if you can't pass a stage. Use one of the several handy power ups which will help you along the way. Collect gems and unlock new amazing designs. Your challenge awaits!

- 20 character design
- Cool powerups: Double gems, Shield and Zero gravity
- Various creative types of gates
- Minimalist and colourful design

title: XTrem FreeStyle 2
description:
Breathtaking acrobatics and even more thrills await you!

Challenge gravity using your best skills! This is the time to make the most dangerous acrobatics and avoid falling in the same time! You can launch yourself in tunnels of sand, lava, ice and many other thrilling environments. Customize your XTrem-Bike and your driver for a special experience. Will you dare to try the impossible?

15 dangerous routes
10 designs to choose from for your bike and driver
Outside and inside camera perspective
Breathtaking acrobatics options

title: Tap the Frog: Doodle
description:
Dozens of diverse frog-popping mini-games in one to keep you busy for hours!

Tap the Frog Doodle features hours of gameplay, diverse mini-games filled with light-hearted humor and achievements to keep you coming back for more. Easy to pick-up yet challenging to master, Tap the Frog Doodle will have your fingers begging for more alone time with the cutest frog on your device. So what are you waiting for? Get tapping!

- 40 levels of frogtastic fun
- Humorous and colourful characters
- Surprising and creative puzzles

title: Dash Masters
description:
Let's save our Earth!

Twenty years ago, the aliens attacked. Billions of lives were lost. We few survivors went underground to create the ultimate weapon that would let us reclaim our planet from this artificial alien race of beings we call ‘Bots.’ Get ready for a true adrenaline rush in this frantic game with dozens of action-packed missions! Fight your way through waves of spiky bots, turrets and moving platforms to the top of the alien battle tower.

- 64 missions full of adventure
- 4 exosuits: Adventurer, Eradicator, Nova and Valkyrie
- Bonus Wheel with extra resources for blasting bots

title: Cut the Rope: Magic Christmas
description:
The Christmas blizzard reveals a new chapter in Om Nom's Magic Book!

Join Om Nom’s newest adventure and transform him into magical forms to help the lovable little monster recover candy stolen by an evil wizard! Christmas is coming, and we couldn't ignore it! Feast your eyes on the shiny Christmas decorations on the map and dive into new adventures with a fresh set of levels. It's the biggest update we've done so far – 40 new levels await you! Have a sweet Christmas!

- 7 maps full of adventure
- Shiny Christmas decorations
- Gorgeous snowflakes that evoke the magic of Christmas

title: Super Dunk Basketball
description:
Become master of the hoop!

Are you ready to shoot high for a slam dunk? Practice your basketball skills and master the game. Collect stars to customize your ball and board and take your chance at the slot machine to unlock new skins. You can play in endless mode, try to beat the clock and score as many points possible, use the walls to bounce the ball into the hoop or shoot through multiple hoops to become the best. Keep training for a super dunk shot!

- 36 fun options to customize balls and boards
- 4 game modes: Endless, Time challenge, Bounce, Multi hoops
- Minimalist design
- Intuitive basketball gameplay

title: Tap the Frog Faster
description:
The Frog is back with new endless gameplay and dozens of challenges!

Ribbit! The legendary Frog is back with all-new addictive gameplay and a dozen of frogsome mini-games to master your frog tapping skills! Get your fingers ready and experience a game that once again redefines the mini-games collection genre with its new endless mode filled with tons of unique challenges. Easy to pick yet challenging to master, this game will keep you coming back for more!

- 15 all-new frogsome mini-games
- Many cool ranks to achieve and share with your friends
- Collect and enhance special cards to get new abilities

Do the math to reach 2048!

Can you stay focused and crunch the numbers to get to a perfect 2048? Swipe to move the numbered tiles as far as possible in any of the four directions on this colourful 4x4 grid. With every turn, a new tile randomly appears in an empty slot with the value of either 2 or 4. When two tiles with the same number touch, they merge into one with the total value. Watch the scoreboard and use your logic!

- Colourful 4x4 grid
- Scoreboard for current and best score
- Fresh and responsive design
- Simple and intuitive gameplay

title: Block vs. Star
description:
Shoot for the stars and slide through the galaxy!

This is the outer space and obstacles lie everywhere… Make your star shine bright through the galaxy and try your best to avoid hitting the surrounding planets. Move your finger across the screen to turn left or right. You can roll with your star or change into a different fun shape. Collect stars along the way to create the longest snake possible. The higher the value of the planet you crash into, the more stars you lose. Sometimes there is no other way than to break right through the planets, so you need as many stars you can get!

- 30 creative skins to choose from
- Static obstacles like planets and rays
- Hypnotizing endless gameplay
- Easy to learn, but challenging to reach high scores
- Vibrant outer space design

title: Snake Smash
description:
Smash blocks & score points!

Welcome to this multicoloured obstacle world! Just slide your way forward, but don’t get too comfortable. Blocks and balls of many values and colours will turn up in your path and challenge your smooth orientation skills. It’s not just left and right, your snake can go in any direction you want in this universe. Increase your multiplier by smashing blocks in quick succession, but don’t get carried away! They may be fun and colourful to smash, but they can still defeat you. Crash into a block with a higher value than your snake’s length and the game’s over! Gathering orange balls gets you points to customize your snake, while others get you extra length. Just stay focused and move your finger across the screen to make sure you survive and smash your way to the highest score!

- 21 skins for your snake
- 9 special challenges 
- Multidirectional gameplay
- Fun and colourful minimalist design

title: Super Dunk Basketball
description:
Become master of the hoop!

Are you ready to shoot high for a slam dunk? Practice your basketball skills and master the game. Collect stars to customize your ball and board and take your chance at the slot machine to unlock new skins. You can play in endless mode, try to beat the clock and score as many points possible, use the walls to bounce the ball into the hoop or shoot through multiple hoops to become the best. Keep training for a super dunk shot!

- 36 fun options to customize balls and boards
- 4 game modes: Endless, Time challenge, Bounce, Multi hoops
- Minimalist design
- Intuitive basketball gameplay

title: Ben 10: Omniverse
description:
Help Ben defeat Psyphon and his mercenaries and save Undertown!

Stop Psyphon from destroying Undertown! The evil Psyphon has planted explosive devices throughout the city and is threatening to detonate them. Ben’s mission is to find and deactivate all of the devices as quickly as possible. Rook, Ben’s new partner, will be joining him on this new adventure. Help Ben defeat Psyphon and his mercenaries and save Undertown!

Battle Psyphon and four different types of mercenaries
Collect maps to help you navigate 3 Undertown neighbourhoods
Use the Omnitrix to transform into Bloxx, Cannonbolt, Feedback and Shocksquatch
Each form has special powers you must harness to accomplish your mission
Enhance your powers by scoring points

title: Gods vs. Humans
description:
Protect the Heavens and be respected by humans!
Humans are building a tower to reach the Kingdom of the Gods! Embody one of these divinities to foil their attempts. But, be careful not to kill them with your special powers, because your survival depends on their devotion! Discover a fun universe and loveable characters from great Nordic, Egyptian, Greco-Roman and Japanese civilisations. Embody 20 ancient Gods and show your followers that you're more than just a myth. You'll need brains, a sense of humour and quick reflexes if you want to become a legend!

- 96 different levels
- 5 legendary mythologies
- 20 playable Gods (Hades, Thor, etc.) 
- 3D production on a 2D map
- Loveable and hilarious characters

title: Guns'n'Glory WW2
description:
Enter the battle and lead your troops to glory!
It’s the winter of 1944, Western Front. You and your boys are on guard duty when the enemy decides to throw wave after wave of troops at your position. Time to man the defences! Recruit and upgrade troops, order tanks into battle and beat the enemy with superior tactics and firepower! Call in air strikes to gain the upper hand and collect supply crates to boost troop morale! Put the heat on the enemy with your flamethrowers and have your medics tend to your soldiers! Take up the guns and earn your glory!

- Thrilling defence-action strategy during WW2
- Successor to the popular Guns’n’Glory Wild West game
- 2 factions to choose from: US Forces, Axis Germany
- 4 different units to recruit on each side
- 12 challenging maps with 3 different difficulty modes
- RPG-like skill system to upgrade your units
- Powerful items to use for tactical advantages
- Earth-shattering explosions and awesome effects
- Pounding battle tunes

title: Hills of Glory 3D
description:
Rifle, mortar, flamethrower, air strikes… don’t hold back!
Lose yourself in Hills of Glory 3D, a WW2 reverse tower defense game with stunning 3D graphics. In this war game, defend your bunker against hordes of enemies with the military arsenal at your disposal. Rifle, mortar, flamethrower, air strikes… don’t hold back! Bring out the Rambo inside you to survive through 21 missions or the Endless mode. Step into the shoes of a military strategist: analyze the battlefield and destroy tactical points to block your enemies’ path. Prove yourself on the battlefield and be promoted to unlock and collect rewards.

- Unique stunning 3D graphics for mainstream tower defense games
- Gain tactical advantages by destroying elements of the map
- 21 missions of increasing difficulty in campaign mode
- 8 weapons (rifle, mortar, flamethrower, napalm, etc.), one anti-infantry bomb and one anti-tank bomb
- Two game modes: Endless and Campaign

title: Slugterra: Dark Waters
description:
Enter the underground world of Slugterra in this breathtaking 3D action game!

Enter the underground world of Slugterra in this breathtaking 3D action adventure game! Based on the animated television series Slugterra, take up the mission of Eli Shane to defend the 99 caverns and become the greatest slugslinger! In this high-tech world beneath your feet, the ammo's alive and only the quick survive. Play as Eli Shane and assemble your team of slugslingers to protect the citizens of Slugterra. Collect an arsenal of little critters called slugs - when you fire them at 100 MPH out of your high-powered blaster, they transform into powerful battle beasts!

- 13 levels
- 4 duel arenas
- 10 unique enemies
- 3 types of gameplay - isometric action, third-person shooter, fighting
- Controllable slugs

title: Ben 10: Vengeance of Vilgax
description:
Face your ultimate challenge!
Face your enemy Vilgax in this brand new Ben 10 beat’em up game. Transform into numerous aliens and battle through 4 unique worlds and 15 action packed levels filled with bioids and drones. Master the mini-games to gain new alien forms and face the vengeance of Vilgax himself.

- Numerous aliens
- 15 action packed levels filled with bioids and drones
- 4 unique worlds

title: 1942 Pacific Front
description:
Experience World War 2 battles in this new military game!
The battle continues after 1941 Frozen Front - and this time, it’s all about naval warfare! Join the navy and fight to win the battle of your life! Own the battlefield and send your soldiers to the frontline. Military combat at its best! Choose the right tactics and use your commando to defeat the enemy! Lead the U.S. Army on their campaign or command the Japanese forces on their mission! Take out enemy alliances with infantry, artillery, tanks, warplanes, battleships and submarines and earn your stripes as an ingenious commander at the PACIFIC FRONT!

- Turn-based strategy action set in WW2
- Thrilling campaigns and challenging missions
- Historical U.S. and Japanese units
- Infantry, artillery, tanks, warplanes, battleships and submarines for both fractions
- Repairs, camouflage and fortification of units during the battles
- Detailed graphics and super-realistic sounds

title: Frankenstein: The Dismembered Bride
description:
Help Brad find the parts of Janet’s body, his fiancée, as well as the pieces of the monstrous machine which will put her body back together… in Frankenstein’s manor! Brad is looking for Janet, who has disappeared for a few months. After a long search, his quest leads him to Bavaria, near a manor house where his car breaks down. Brad discovers that the house is owned by a weird scientist: Lord Albrecht von Frankenstein. Janet has been his last “experiment”. She’s still alive, but her body has been set apart, and all the parts have been scattered around the house. Brad has to find them, and all the missing pieces of the machine that can put Janet’s body together again. Discover all the rooms of the manor in their every detail: the greenhouse, the torture room, the cemetery. Their realism will make you hold your breath!

- 23 screens to examine
- Free navigation 
- Search for objects
- x2 zoom and reloading hints
- Magnificent sets and high-resolution images

title: Tanks vs. Aliens
description:
There are various scenes in the game, such as jungle, military bases, snowfield and doomsday. Every map has thrilling Boss mode with unique gameplay. There are various tanks with different firepower for you to select. You can select a suitable operation mode from touch screen or gravity sensor. It is simple and easy to play. You will love this game!

- Exquisite graphics
- Passionate music
- Smooth game control
- Feature levels bring you fun

title: C.I.A. Petrodollars
description:
Bring down the people that think they're above the law.
At the center of the famous government agency, the "Federal Tax Bureau" (a.k.a. the "F.T.B."), is a team dedicated to the most serious affairs - the “Criminal Investigation Service”. You play the role of F.T.B. Special Agent, Frances Keegan. Responsible for tracking down tax evaders in three-piece suits, your heroine knows the financial world, spy techniques and on-site investigations like the back of her hand. Specialised in the oil industry, Frances is relentlessly pursuing Klaus Fredricks, who has been under constant surveillance ever since he was suspected of murdering one of the agents' colleagues and friends, Eric Ward. The scale of the operation is getting larger, and the F.T.B. is doing everything in its power to catch all those who think they are above any man and any law.

- An original storyline
- A breathtaking plot
- Stunningly realistic animated scenery
- Zoom in and move around scenes easily to unearth clues
- Customize the heroine according to the various assignments
- Various mini games such as Match 3, Sliding Block and Jigsaw games

title: Prince of Persia: the Shadow and the Flame
description:
Embark on legendary adventures with the Prince of Persia!

Witness the rebirth of the legendary action-platformer, with brand-new visuals and controls redesigned to fit your device. Prince of Persia The Shadow and the Flame continues the saga of the wanderer who was born a Prince. Now he must embark on an epic journey in search of his past that will redefine his future! Discover an exciting new combat system with multiple enemies and tactical challenges! Enjoy an immersive game, an exciting combat system, and intuitive controls for mobile!

14 levels rendered in visually-stunning 3D 
Dive into 5 state-of-the-art environments
Unleash devastating combos and unlock even more powerful ones as you progress
Acquire new weapons for increasingly thrilling fight sequences

title: Lara Croft: Relic Run
description:
Lara Croft: Relic Run is all new adventure for nostalgic Lara Croft fans!
When a shadowy conspiracy threatens the world, only Lara Croft is equipped to unearth the truth. Run, swing, drive, and swan dive your way through beautiful and challenging environments, uncovering ancient relics to discover the truth and solve the mystery. Each location is filled with secrets and danger. Progress through the campaign map to collect relics and advance the Relic Run story. Use parkour moves to create death-defying last minute escapes. Master fast-paced vehicles like ATVs and motorcycles to give Lara more ways to conquer the terrain. There’s no time to waste, but how long can you survive?

- 3 incredible locations: Jungle Temple, Desert and the new Mountain Pass - each filled with secrets and danger
- Progress through the campaign map to collect relics and advance the Relic Run story
- Endless mode for non-stop action and the chance to rack up big rewards
- Power up Lara’s arsenal of weapons and engage in frantic combat
- Use parkour moves to create death-defying last minute escapes
- Master fast-paced vehicles like ATVs and motorcycles to give Lara more ways to conquer the terrain
- Epic Boss Fights - defeat iconic enemies including the return of the infamous T-Rex
- Swap and upgrade equipment to give Lara the edge
- Choose from a wardrobe of classic Lara outfits, each with its own gameplay perks

title: Double Dragon I
description:
Enjoy one of the '80s most popular arcade games for the 1st time on mobile!

A groundbreaking, uber-popular game upon its arcade debut in 1987, Double Dragon is the undisputed godfather of co-op beat'em all! The adventure begins with Billy and his brother Jimmy, two martial arts experts, in a mission to rescue Billy's girlfriend, Marian, who’s been kidnapped by the Black Shadows Gang. Battle your way through this and bask in the greatness of one of the '80s most popular arcade games!

3 difficulty levels: Mobile, Original and Expert
2 game modes: Arcade and Story
Customizable controls
Various surprising moves for your character

title: Raiden Legacy
description:
Put your skills to the test with the popular Raiden Legacy!

RAIDEN LEGACY, a four-title compilation of the mega-popular RAIDEN arcade series, includes RAIDEN, RAIDEN FIGHTERS, RAIDEN FIGHTERS 2 & RAIDEN FIGHTERS JET. Originally developed by Seibu Kaihatsu, each of these classic scrolling shooters has not only been authentically recreated for mobile but also enhanced with brand-new features! Put your skills to the test against your friends, family and the best players in the world!

15+ different ships, each with their own characteristics, stats, weapons, and specials
3 modes for each Raiden title
2 different touch modes: Fast Touch and Arcade Touch

title: R-Type
description:
One of the biggest arcade game will make you travel back in the day!

Let's go back in the 80's with this classic old-school shoot'em up! Be ready to have fun with this old-school side-shooter game! The game is the challenging R-Type you used to play before. And we kept all its specifics, just the way you remember it! Upgrade with new weapons, power-ups, and attachments. Blast off and strike the evil Bydo Empire! Don't be shy and use your best shot to take them down! It's retro, it's fun and it's also hard to master. Be the best ever to finish this masterpiece!

8 unique bosses and waves of various enemies
8 levels with 3 different control options
2 difficulty levels

title: Deadly Fighter
description:
Become a hero and the most powerful fighter in the world!
Your village was raided, only you can save local people. Don’t waste the time, and fight! The world's largest fighting contest is started. No ranking, no rules, only dead or alive! Who is the strongest fighter on the earth? Plunge into epic combat sequences rendered in astonishingly lifelike detail. Journey through four different locations - and just try to survive in this uncalculable, full of the magic world. But remember, it’s a place where speed and skills matter! Choose your fighter, unlock, buy and upgrade boosts. Become a hero and the most powerful fighter in the world!

- Amazing graphics
- 4 stunning sceneries
- Great music and sounds
- 12 unlockable boosts

title: Hospital Manager
description:
Head up a one-of-a-kind hospital and embark on the path to success!
Experience something novel, bursting with extraordinary phenomena and strange situations in your hospital! Only you have the power to make the best decisions and to make your hospital the most popular one! But beware: Several events will add some spice to your life! Embark on the career of your life! Choose and hire your doctors and employees, build the departments of your choosing, and manage your finances! Are you thrifty or a big spender? Would you rather pamper your patients instead of your banker? Make your own decisions! You'll have many missions to accomplish, littered with all kinds of epidemics, patients with disturbing pathologies such as the zombie disease, the Chewbacca syndrome, and the moonwalk virus. Be on the lookout: Many events will spice up your rise, such as exterminating extraterrestrial germs and stopping toad contamination! Customize your hospital down to the last details, buy high-tech equipment, choose rooms that will make your hospital center the most popular one!

- Use comprehensive management of your hospital to your advantage: You're the boss
- Build your reputation with a large variety of factors
- Accomplish diverse and surprising missions
- Plunge into an explosive 3D cartoon style universe with wacky pathologies and situations
- Experience a nonlinear adventure: Every decision will lead to different consequences, depending on when the action happens
- A rich system of artificial intelligence that can adapt patient behaviour to each of your actions and decisions

title: R-Type II
description:
Have some fun with this classic old-school game!

R-Type II is a horizontal scrolling shooter arcade game developed and published by Irem in 1989. This classic old-school game is the sequel to R-Type and the story takes place two years after. The player controls a ship called the R-9C which is an improved version of its predecessor, the R-9. Beware because the Bydo Empire is back! Take it down with power-ups, two new types of weapons, the Search Laser and Shotgun Laser, and a new anti-ground unit bomb.

6 levels each with its own unique boss
Upgrade to new weapons, power-ups, and attachments to fight wave of enemies
3 difficulty settings: unlimited, normal & insane
2 control modes: Touch and virtual D-Pad

title: Baseball vs. Zombies
description:
Get you baseball team ready to smash this blood-thirsty zombie apocalypse!
Are you ready to defend the Stadium and kill some zombies? Your only defence is the team present in the stadium. Use various advantages like Hitter, Pitchers, Coach, Cheer leaders and Ball machines to kill zombies. Use Grass cutter, Team Attack and Chopper for mob killing and nullify the danger. Make your own strategy and just follow the instructions and defeat the zombies and be the saviour. Experience the sensation of killing zombies wildly!

- 5 different types of zombies
- 5 different types of players
- 3 types of special powers for mass killing

title: Safe Cracker
description:
Penetrate the inner systems of a secure vault, bouncing Nano around the mechanisms and solving puzzles! Tilt or touch your device to rotate the level, and use physics to your advantage as you avoid bouncers and lasers. Don't get frazzled! Extensive replayability: can you collect all three stars AND the time trophy for all the levels? Features amazing artwork from a BAFTA-award winning animator, and a catchy original soundtrack!

- 128 action-packed puzzle
- 16 varied layers
- The world's most secure vault

title: Zombie Rising
description:
The war against the undead! Kill every zombie you see! You will enter a world far beyond your imagination with a huge variety of zombie enemies and challenging gameplay. Test yourself through 20 expertly designed levels and save the world from the zombie infestation.

- Colourful graphics
- Multiple weapons & upgrades
- Simple but highly addictive gameplay
- Guarantee of maximum excitement

title: Evoland
description:
A short story of adventure video games evolution.
Evoland is an action adventure game which takes you on a journey through the history of classic adventure and RPG gaming. As you progress through the game, you unlock new technologies, gameplay systems and ever-improving graphics. From monochrome to full 3D graphics and from turn-based battles to real time boss fights, Evoland makes you live the evolution of adventure gaming - all with plenty of humour and nods to moments from classic games.

- Play through the history of action-adventure video games
- Starting area rendered in full 3D or an exploration of the overworld with your own airship
- Various evolutions, from old school 2D action/adventure to active time battles and full 3D action
- Dungeons, puzzles, a heap of secrets to uncover, and hundreds of achievements and stars to collect

title: Deus Ex GO
description:
An unique take on this near future dystopian world!
Challenge all-new turn-based logic puzzles and solve a futuristic mystery in this tactical board game. Adventure through an intricate and mysterious storyline set in a beautiful vision of the future! Puzzles in Deus Ex GO challenge you to utilize a mixture of stealth, espionage and raw intelligence as you guide secret agent Adam Jensen across a visually stunning storyline. Sneak, hack and fight your way past enemies, and augment Adam with futuristic upgrades to solve the most intricate puzzles!

50 unique puzzles in a mysterious new storyline
Futuristic scenery
Turn invisible, hack enemy turrets and even change the layout of the map itself

title: 9 Elephants
description:
Follow our two intrepid investigators across Paris as you've never seen it before, a combination of fantasy and the Crazy Years. Converse with colourful characters with secrets to share. Solve over 230 puzzles to reveal the secret of the 9 elephants. Plunge into the heart of the capital, and savour this extraordinary tale featuring a modern art exhibition, poisoned oranges, a magician's cat, a cyclist, an accordion champion, an esoteric conspiracy, the Paris catacombs, the destruction of the Eiffel Tower and... 9 elephants.

- Solve over 230 puzzles with 8 different gameplays
- Explore Paris's most enigmatic locations
- Encounter 20 delightful and mysterious characters, 
including a cat
- Savour the city's fascinating atmosphere

title: A Girl in the City
description:
With her journalism degree in her pocket, Laura leaves her small-town home to take a bite out of the Big Apple! She dreams of becoming a freelance journalist with a major New York women’s magazine, but the road is long and fraught with pitfalls…And what about love in all of this? Discover New York and help Laura achieve her goal! Seek out information on the busy life of New Yorkers in order to write good articles, meet new people and become the most prominent columnist! Make the most of the 2x zoom to delve deeper into the images, and use the clues to better locate objects. Are you short on clues or time? Flush out bonus stars hidden in the pictures to earn some more!

- Interactive inventory
- Search for a variety of dynamic, animated objects (lists, silhouettes, charades…)
- Numerous places to inspect
- Mini-games: puzzles, reflex games
- Management of 3 personalized profiles
- Ability to upload scores online
- Help: zoom in on certain screens, limited reloadable clues, bonus stars
- Luxurious decor: high-definition images

title: A Vampire Romance
description:
Leïla Saraostre, a young foreigner, moves in a famous Parisian neighbourhood, Montmartre, to study at the art school of the Louvre. There she meets Uriel Ruthven, a young and enigmatic man. She quickly falls in love. He takes her around and makes her discover the bright city, Paris, before disappearing mysteriously…Discover Uriel’s strange secret!

- 40 places to observe
- Mini-games: decipher a coded message; find your way in catacombs…
- Search of objects (list, identical objects)
- Help: zoom on selected screens, limited number of reloading hints, bonus stars
- Magnificent sets: high-resolution images

title: Fractal Combat X
description:
There’s now a simulator flight mode that allows to do all sort of manoeuvres that a jet fighter can do. There is also an ample choice of vehicles, an intuitive upgrade system and much improved 3D graphics. FCX shines on the latest generation devices, with its realistic lighting model and impressive explosion effects.
The game offers a ton of gameplay, a story mode with 6 worlds to explore plus daily missions made of randomly generated worlds. The progressive level of difficulty makes it easy to jump in but should keep busy even the toughest gamer out there.

- Exciting, fast-paced arcade flight combat action
- Top notch 3D graphics
- Unique gorgeous fractal landscapes
- Dozens of missions in Story mode

title: Ben 10: Ultimate Alien Defender
description:
The evil Aggregor is trying to become all powerful by absorbing the powers of other aliens. He is also attacking your friends Kevin and Gwen with his robots. Protect your friends and stop Aggregor before all is lost!

- Protect your friends
- Addictive gameplay

title: Casino Crime
description:
Manage a Mafia casino and swindle your punters out of their money. It's an offer you can't refuse! Start your criminal career in the glamorous world of gambling! Help luck along a little in your own casino and take your guests to the cleaners! Whether it's easy pickpocketing or elaborate card tricks: the only good guest is a fleeced guest! With your foot on the brake of the roulette wheel and an ace up your sleeve, you're ready for anything. Welcome to the family!

- Exciting casino manager game with Mafia connections
- Slot machines, Blackjack and Roulette
- Use dirty tricks to cheat your punters
- Pick pockets to earn some quick money
- Unscrupulous croupiers with a talent for crime

title: Robin Hood the Prince
description:
Help the young Robin as he retells his adventures through a magical land full of evil genies, possessed enemies and a mad Sultan. Enjoy a whole new adventure spanning 10 chapters, with new and familiar faces, engaging quests, bosses and a new arsenal.

- A magical land
- Evil genies possessed enemies and a mad Sultan
- 10 chapters

title: Slot Machine 2
description:
If you enjoy free slot machine games, then Slot machine 2 is the game for you. Beautiful classic slot style gameplay comes with juicy fruits and big wins. Play free slots with Wilds, Free Spins and Bonus game feaures like in Vegas. Just spin the wheels and try your luck!

- Big wins
- Double chance
- Beautiful graphic
- Simple gameplay
- Bonus game

title: Townsmen 6
description:
Conquer France's Départments by creating villages and complete the tasks set to you. Construct buildings, like fisher huts, farms, forges or bakeries to sustain a solid economic cycle. Catch fish, harvest fields, get water and use various natural resources that are needed to expand your influence. Upgrade your buildings, learn new ways to improve the productivity and spread out on the French territory. Control your Townies and assign them to different tasks to manage your settlement in the most efficient way, but respect their needs to keep them and their wives happy.

- Complex build-up strategy game
- Detailed simulation of the Townies and Townettes
- Prepare the Townsmen for the battle against the French king
- Extensive tutorial and help functions for easy access
- Cute Townsmen graphics
- Weather effects affecting game mechanics

title: Blake and Mortimer: The Curse of the Thirty Denarii
description:
Mortimer has just been contacted to inspect a huge archaeological discovery in Greece: Judas’ thirty denarii! Nearly 2000 years ago, the apostle Judas betrayed Christ to the Romans for thirty denarii. The silver coins contain a deadly curse to anyone who touches them. In the wrong hands, such a dangerous artefact could spell disaster for the entire human race… Blake and Mortimer must find the missing denarii before any blood is shed again. Fearless as always, Blake and Mortimer return in this thrilling new adventure!

- Interactive inventory and parallax
- Numerous places to investigate
- Various mini-games: puzzles, match 3 game
- Incredible high definition graphics

title: Gladiator Escape
description:
Gladiator has escaped from the Jail of the Coliseum to find his beloved wife. The escape is not that easy. Help him to escape and avoid the traps lying in his way. Run through the puzzling ways. Choose your path wisely. Then jump, slide and swing to kill enemies. You will encounter the gladiators scouts which set to capture and kill the gladiator. Fight with them and defeat them. Play this amazing escape and fighting gladiator runner game with gorgeous graphics and different game styles.

- 30 easy escape levels
- 20 hard escape levels
- 3 different exciting worlds

title: Zombie Busters
description:
Get ready to lead the Squadron of Zombie Busters, a team of deadly zombie killers who have summoned for fighting the zombie apocalypse on Earth! Each hero has its own unique abilities and powers so as zombies. Plan your strategy well ahead, make the right decision and fight well! Perfect your skills and unleash stunning Special Attacks so as to destroy Tsunami of zombies.  It’s a deadly clash between Zombie Buster Squad against an army of evils in the city. Get ready to make a bloody nightmare for the undead units! Plenty of power-ups and upgrades are available, upgrade your weapons and abilities, defence of the kingdom is now in your hand. Different challenges such as Defend the buildings, Help the survivor’s allies, locate the objects, destroy the tower and reach the destination and many more.

- 50+ addicting levels with hours of fun
- 3 different heroes equipped with many types of ammunition such as - ground cutter, jetpack, slicer, grenade launcher and many more
- Various deadly powerful guns for killing zombies
- Modern battle via various strong guns and stunning ambience

title: Mafia vs. Monsters
description:
The Mafia comes across a mysterious treasure, a long-lost sacred idol. The Don takes it as a sign of good luck and decides to keep it for themselves. Little does the Mafia knew that it is long lost legendary idol to some creature coming from monsters world. Soon enough, nasty monsters find out and launch an attack. It’s time to load up the guns and blow the crap out of thousands of brainless monsters and deadly bosses! You must not only survive but also lead, be careful, fight and defend. Grew your mafia team by unlocking new exciting mafia upgrades and solve the puzzle. Your mission is to hold your ground against the ruthless monster zombies to crush and eliminate them. Command your Mafia gang with deadly power-ups. This game has all best elements of Tower defender games and much more. You will have to use your mafia team as the ally to get a glorious victory. Use gangsters as defenders and smash down the zombie monsters.

- 50 levels of glorious victories against blood-thirsty monster apocalypse
- Different strong gangsters to defeat monster hordes
- Various powers like electrifying and zapping monsters

title: Double Dragon II: The Revenge
description:
Get the best of your martial arts skills!

Enjoy one of the ‘80s most popular arcade games and get your revenge! Billy and his brother Jimmy are back in action. All your favourite moves are here: punches, kicks, elbows, knees, head-butts and an assortment of not-exactly-street-legal weapons.

3 difficulty levels: Mobile, Original and Expert
2 game modes: Arcade and Story
Original 8-bit soundtrack and a brand-new remastered one

title: Double Dragon III: The Rosetta Stone
description:
Enter one of the most beloved arcade worlds!

It's time for a new mission in the world of martial arts! Billy and his brother Jimmy are using all their best moves: punches, kicks, elbows, knees, head-butts and an assortment of not-exactly-street-legal weapons. Battle your way through all 3 titles and enjoy the greatness of one of the ‘80s most popular arcade games!

3 difficulty levels: Mobile, Original and Expert
2 game modes: Arcade and Story
Customizable controls

title: Deadly Association
description:
Nancy Boyle, a young woman without a criminal past has been found dead half-naked near her home in Brooklyn. The forensic police inspectors Chloé and Paul are on the case. There's a big surprise in store for them. This case is full of developments that keep Chloé Cunningham and Paul Baxter on their toes. You'll need to use your investigation skills and attention to detail in this investigation. Use your expert criminology equipment to shed light on the mystery of these repeated murders, reveal clues lurking in the shadows, and most importantly - track down your target - the truth. Every room, place, and the protagonist is key to the case. If you want to have any hope of piecing together this puzzle - which is not looking easy at all - pay attention to these clues. The twist and turns of this investigation abound in riddles and hidden objects.

- Animated settings and production
- An original thriller script
- Interactive inventory
- Several mini games: Puzzles, Match-3

title: Dr Jekyll and Mr Hyde
description:
At the end of the 19th century, a monster is prowling around in the Victorian fog of London. He has trampled on a young girl, killed a Member of Parliament, and molested a match seller. When he finds out the terrible news, Mr Utterson ends up discovering that the case is not unrelated to his friend Dr Henry Jekyll and to the terrible individual currently staying with him: Mr Hyde. Step into Mr Utterson’s shoes and set off on the trail of Mr Hyde. Finally, discover the ghastly link that connects Dr Jekyll with this Mr Hyde! Can it be broken? Up to you to play! Make the most of the 2x zoom to delve deeper into the images, and use the clues to better locate objects. Are you short on clues or time? Flush out bonus stars hidden in the pictures to earn some more! Move around in Dr Jekyll’s house, his laboratory, and the labyrinth city of London to get to the bottom of this mystery and to try to save Dr Jekyll from the danger stalking him.

- Interactive inventory
- Search for a variety of dynamic, animated objects
- Numerous places to inspect
- Mini-games: puzzles, reflex games
- Management of 3 personalized profiles
- Luxurious decor: high-definition images

title: FBI: Paranormal Case
description:
James is a young FBI agent newly promoted to the Department of Unclosed Case Files. During his different enquiries into strange cases, he uncovers an incredible international plot that aims to hide a shocking and well-guarded secret. Search for clues and help the enquiry to move forward, counter sabotage attempts, find evidence of the plot and bring light into the mysterious secret behind these paranormal events! Take advantage of the 2x zoom to get inside the pictures and use the clue to help locate the search area for one of the objects. Don’t have the clue or not enough time? Uncover the bonus stars hidden in the paintings in order to win them! Visit unusual and surprising places all over the world, from an abandoned laboratory to the Bermuda Triangle!

-  40 places to inspect
- Mini-games: puzzles, reflexive games
- Manage 3 customizable profiles
- Search for objects (lists, identical objects)
- Help: zoom in on certain screens, limited reloadable clues, bonus stars
- Sumptuous settings: high-definition pictures

title: Jack the Ripper: Letters from Hell
description:
It is London during the summer of 1888. On the hunt for spicy stories, the reporter Bert goes on the trail of Jack the Ripper, the famous serial killer that is terrorising the White Chapel district. He goes as far as falsifying letters from Jack the Ripper and sends them to the police. But his involvement in this affair soon makes him the ideal suspect for the police at Scotland Yard. Help Bert prove his innocence and conduct his own investigation in order to clear up the mystery of the White Chapel killer! The Police are keeping a close eye on Bert, so you will have to help him with his mission. Closely examine the sites, find proof, take photos, develop them, and draw on your memory to prove that the real Jack the Ripper is elsewhere. Use the x2 zoom to dive into the heart of the images and the clue to recover the objects you need. Discover the sleazy districts and dark alleyways of 19th century London: White Chapel, Buck’s Row, Hanbury street, Bernet street, Mitre square, Miller’s court.

- 30 sites to see
- Mini games: observation, logic, memory
- Manage 3 customisable profiles
- Object search (list, identical objects)
- Unlimited help: x2 zoom, reloadable clue
- Sumptuous scenery: high definition images

title: Jennifer Wolf and the Mayan Relics
description:
Jennifer Wolf leaves San Francisco to join her father on the archaeological dig he is leading in Mexico. When she arrives on site, she can’t find any trace of him and all his belongings have been ransacked. Prior to his disappearance, he managed to hide a certain manuscript - a book, dating from the 16th century, telling of the last sacred Mayan calendar which had been broken up into five separate fragments and entrusted to selected guardians to ensure its protection. You play the role of Jennifer Wolf. It is now your mission to find your father and these precious Mayan relics. With the help of Raphael, your father’s assistant, it is now down to you to solve the mystery. You will examine archaeological sites, cross the Mexican jungle, take an in-depth look at Monument Valley, pursue your investigation as far as Washington, seek out advice from a friend in Navajo, and uncover yet more secrets in a wide range of locations steeped in mystery.

- An original storyline
- Historical locations
- A keep-you-guessing plot
- Realistic screenshots
- Varied soundtrack
- Several mini games to unlock

title: Public Enemies: Bonnie & Clyde
description:
1933. Janette Jones Parker is a writer and has taken a room in the Red Crown Tavern in Platte City, Missouri, to write her next novel. She discovers it is where Bonnie & Clyde used to hide, and there she finds a notebook, which ends to be Bonnie’s log. Help Janette to decipher the strange message left by Bonnie along her journey! Go through the United States, on the tracks of the two outlaws! Follow the tremendous adventure of the “#1-public-enemies-couple”, reconstitute the logbook of their adventure and discover the secrets of their map! Use the Hint: a shiny halo helps you to find one of the objects. No more hints? Not enough time? Find the bonus stars hidden in the scenes to get more hints or time! Examine meticulously the various places of passage of the two criminals: a hotel room, a bar, a garage, a camp of refugees, banks. All in the respect of the style of the 30s!

- 47 places to observe
- Mini-games: re-build a firearm, decode messages
- Search of objects (list, identical objects)
- Help: zoom on selected screens, limited number of reloading hints, bonus stars
- Magnificent sets: high resolution images

title: Secrets of the Vatican
description:
Among all the relics spread across the world, the Holy Lance of Longin is considered to be the most wanted one. This weapon, which would have leaked out the side of Jesus during his crucifixion, would bring victory to the men who possess it. Father Bellarmo Bagatti, an art historian of the Church of Roma, is in charge of a mission of the highest importance: get the Holy Lance back before Germans seize it. The ending of World War II is depending on your success. Explore a chapel in Paris, ruins in Istanbul, a monastery in Roma, or a church in Berlin. Discover all the sceneries in the greatest detail!

- 24 places to visit around the world
- Search of objects (of a list, identical objects, to collect)
- Unlimited help: x2 zoom, reloading hints
- Magnificent sets: high-resolution images

title: Profiler
description:
Examine the crime scenes, find clues and discover the serial killer identity. Will you be able to find him on time? Miss Smith will soon be replacing Deckard, a police officer who is retiring. He will still be here a few days, to show her the ropes. And they won’t be resting: several cases are waiting for them. Obviously, it is more about murders than accidents or suicides… The murderer seems to be following a precise pattern… Miss Black and Deckard will have to investigate to discover who the serial killer is and prevent him from killing someone else. Prove you are a good profiler to your NYPD boss!

- 40 screens to examine
- Mini-games: 20 differences, secret code to decipher, anonymous messages to decode
- Search of objects (of a list, identical objects, to collect)
- Unlimited help: x2 zoom, reloading hints
- Magnificent sets: high resolution images

title: The Princess Case: A Royal Scoop
description:
The media were all smiles as the royal couple set off on their honeymoon trip. A reporter with New York’s People Mag, Lois Wheeler was the first on the trail of a big exclusive. But when she finds her way into the newly-weds' hotel, Lois gets more than she bargained for. Instead of interviewing the couple of the moment, she finds herself tangled up in an international kidnapping case. And before she knows it the FBI are involved. Thrown into a situation unlike any she has faced in her career, Lois has to use her investigative skills and gift for languages to rise to the occasion. Seek out the objects used to commit the kidnapping and begin your investigation. Use your reporting skills and powers of observation and deduction to evade the trickiest of situations.

- A host of superb animated scenes
- An original storyline
- Simple and intuitive gameplay
- An interactive inventory
- A range of mini games: Puzzles, Match 3, Sliding Blocks

title: The Bluecoats: North vs South
description:
Head up the Yankees or Confederates and destroy your enemy! Taking up positions, capturing states, assaulting and capturing enemy forts, attacking trains and protecting your railroads... you'll have to deal with everything! Capture the port to use the reinforcements coming from Europe. Protect yourself from storms and be wary of ambushes and bandits. To come out in one piece, you'll have to master taking turns, armed battles in real time, 1 against 30 shoot-outs, and horseback train chases in this colourful strategy game!

- Dynamic and strategic battles
- Several mini games
- Multiplayer mode

title: XIII: Lost Identity
description:
Imagine waking up to discover you’ve led several different lives. A man suffering from amnesia is found washed up on a beach by an elderly couple. He has to unravel who he is and where he has come from, the only clue to his identity being the numerals “XIII” tattooed on his neck. Pursued by mysterious strangers and wanted for the assassination of the President of the United States of America, his life becomes a whirl of conspiracy and intrigue. Pay close attention to everything around you, because it will no doubt be your only chance to piece together XIII’s enigmatic past.

- Superb, realistic animated scenes adapted from the comic book series itself
- Simple and intuitive gameplay
- An interactive inventory
- A range of mini games: Puzzles, Match 3, Sliding Blocks

title: Hungry Shark Evolution
description:
Take control of a very Hungry Shark, and have the ocean become your playground!
Take control of a very Hungry Shark in this action packed aquatic adventure in 3D! Survive as long as possible by eating everything that gets in your way! You have many different sharks to collect and evolve, including the Hammerhead, Great White and Megalodon! Equip your sharks with special gadgets and items. Unlock Baby Sharks to boost your predatory powers. Enjoy more than 75 missions and 14 sharks!

3D graphics
14 Shark types to unlock
Intuitive touch or tilt controls
15 sunken Bonus Objects to discover
Over 75 missions to complete

title: Assassin’s Creed Unity: Arno's Chronicles
description:
For the first time, enjoy the stunning action license on your Android phone!

Enjoy an immersive action game, packaged in an ideal size for your mobile, and faithful to the console core features and spirit. Discover outstanding graphics, travelling in various mythical environments inside Paris city while you play Arno Dorian, in his hunt to find his father’s murderer. Enjoy multiple gameplays: run on Paris’ rooftops or jump in the trees of Tuileries’ garden, fight with numerous enemies that will try to stop you in your hunt, mastering your sword or shooting! But always keep in mind that your best chances will be to remain discreet and kill your enemies without being detected…

- 20 levels of adventure in 18th century Paris
- Thrilling attack options like Stealth assassination, Gun shooting, Bomb throwing and Attack combinations 
- Multiple enemies & bosses to face in combat
- Hawkeye mode for finding clues
- Stunning environments of famous French landmarks

title: Total Recoil
description:
Classic arcade style, high octane, top down shoot ‘em up!

Look lively soldier! Grab your gear and fall in line for the biggest, baddest, craziest and most explosive war game to hit your screens and assault your senses. Total Recoil takes arcade shooters to the max; it’s a warmongers delight, packing a deadly arsenal of kick-ass weapons, devastating explosions, mega bosses, and much, much more into one dynamite package.

- 3 game modes: Operations, Rank Challenges and Endless Wave
- Explosively addictive arcade gameplay
- Upgradable weapons including Assault Rifle, Flamethrower, Chaingun, Cannon, Grenade Launcher and Missile Launcher
- ‘Killstreak’ rewards including artillery strikes, sentry guns and dive bombing planes
